==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fatally
<hw>Fa"tal*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In a
manner proceeding from, or determined by, fate.</def>
<rj><au>Bentley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In a manner resulting in death or ruin; mortally;
destructively; <as>as, <ex>fatally</ex> deceived or
wounded</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fatalness</ent>⟦br⟧
